{"tid":1806254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【元旦大遊行】警方灣仔東區拘 5 名男子　涉藏有攻擊武器　最細 13 歲","createTime":"2020-01-01T07:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T07:58:10.000Z","uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6adabef2dde278c52b6291108c668d0b36051516","tid":1806254,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"民陣今日發起「元旦大遊行」，但早在遊行起步前，防暴警員於遊行路線的修頓球場外制服及帶走最少一人，未知詳細原因。警方表示，今日中午先後於灣仔區及東區拘捕五名男子，被捕人士年齡最細 13 歲，並以「藏有攻擊性武器」罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方下午三時半左右於 Facebook 表示，今日中午先後於灣仔區及東區拘捕五名男子，被捕人士年齡最細 13 歲，涉嫌藏有伸縮棍、槌子、士巴拿和鐵蓮花等攻擊性武器，被警方以「藏有攻擊性武器」罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱昨日於黃大仙一個山坡檢獲大量汽油彈原材料，不排除有人計劃於今日遊行期間「製造事端」，危害公眾安全。警方又呼籲遊行人士注意自身安全。<br />\n<br />\n今日大約下午 2 時半，警方在灣仔修頓球場對出制服最少一名男子，並搜查男子的背包，大批防暴警員在軒尼詩道築防線，防止他人走近。有警員在現場用擴音器表示，較早前發現有人藏有武器，目前他們正調查案件。有警員一度用胡椒噴劑指向現場的市民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E6%8B%98-5-%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-%E6%B6%89%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B0-13-%E6%AD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258B%2598-5-%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8-%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B4%25B0-13-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIcybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=37d5631c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258B%2598-5-%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8-%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B4%25B0-13-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&h=7c155ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E6%8B%98-5-%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-%E6%B6%89%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B0-13-%E6%AD%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"1fbe45300256d8f5942a1fc57016781c62587045","tid":1806254,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bf2d4e90b56ba397ff7e6dfa6a6766c93dbd786c","tid":1806254,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82fc748548a9418daffce7cc6d0d22d41f634aa","tid":1806254,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2eba57ea2323a22ed4abb653d933e6fea6cf6e79","tid":1806254,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0ccd3042e082e10f890aefd1bbd1904bc4af1661","tid":1806254,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc511de530a446bd8b3c0059266d372ec702f19c","tid":1806254,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong>"},{"pid":"aeeb852ba421243243b069526a03106841b816a8","tid":1806254,"uid":3172